info.name: P1999 --P1999 skin  fix
info.description: This is just a very small fix for the --P1999 skin (not the default blue skin).  It changes the small subheading text to a visible gray.  Only putting this up so people don't need to hassle with creating it themselves.
info.additionalInfo: The default p1999 skin blows my eyes out the back of my head at night.
